SeaCoast University – README
Project made by Dillon Cool, Robert Deleon, Jahaziel Guerrero
Overview
FancySignup is a simple ASP.NET Core web application that demonstrates:
* User signup

* User login

* SQLite storage

* Basic admin dashboard

* Custom password validation


* MVC architecture (Models, Views, Controllers)
________________


Data Storage
This project uses SQLite for class and student storage.
________________


Password Rules
Passwords must:
   * Start with a letter

   * Contain at least one uppercase letter

   * Contain at least one lowercase letter

   * Contain at least one digit

   * Be at least 8 characters long

Example valid password:
Abcdef12


________________


Demo Logins
Admin Login
Username: admin
Password: Admin123!
________________


How to Run
From the project folder:
dotnet run


The app launches on:
https://localhost:5000


(Port numbers may vary depending on your machine.)
________________


Features
User Signup
      * Validates password rules

      * Prevents duplicate emails

User Login
         * Compares input credentials to users stored in database

         * Redirects to profile page after login

Admin Dashboard
            * Protected admin-only login

            * View all registered users

            * Delete users

            * Basic user stats

            * Reads directly from users.txt

________________


